  <entry>
    <id>http://arxiv.org/abs/cond-mat/9704223v1</id>
    <updated>1997-04-28T04:44:59Z</updated>
    <published>1997-04-28T04:44:59Z</published>
    <title>Quasi-Langevin method for shot noise calculation in single-electron
  tunneling</title>
    <summary>  It is shown that quasi-Langevin method can be used for the calculation of the
shot noise in correlated single-electron tunneling. We generalize the existing
Fokker-Plank-type approach and show its equivalence to quasi-Langevin approach.
The advantage of the quasi-Langevin method is a natural possibility to describe
simultaneously the high (``quantum'') frequency range.
</summary>
    <author>
      <name>Alexander N. Korotkov</name>
    </author>
    <arxiv:doi xmlns:arxiv="http://arxiv.org/schemas/atom">10.1209/epl/i1998-00363-0</arxiv:doi>
