    <title>Electronic Transport in La-Ca Manganites</title>
    <summary>  We revisit the transport properties of La-Ca manganites in detail, since they
have been confirmed in a number of CMR-exhibiting materials. We also discuss
new data considered the hallmark of an unusually high electron-phonon coupling
responsible for charge localization and small polaron transport.
</summary>
