    <title>Resonant electronic Raman scattering near a quantum critical point</title>
    <summary>  We calculate the resonant electronic Raman scattering for the Falicov-Kimball
model near the Mott transition on a hypercubic lattice. The solution is exact,
and employs dynamical mean field theory.
