    <title>Mean-field phase diagram of interacting e_g electrons</title>
    <summary>  We investigate the magnetic phase diagram of the two-dimensional model for
e_g electrons which describes layered nickelates. One finds a generic tendency
towards magnetic order accompanied by orbital polarization. For two equivalent
orbitals with diagonal hopping such orbitally polarized phases are induced by
finite crystal field.
</summary>
    <author>
      <name>M. Raczkowski</name>
    </author>
    <author>
      <name>A. M. Oles</name>
    </author>
