    <title>The electron density is smooth away from the nuclei</title>
    <summary>  We prove that the electron densities of electronic eigenfunctions of atoms
and molecules are smooth away from the nuclei.
</summary>
    <author>
      <name>S. Fournais</name>
    </author>
    <author>
      <name>M. Hoffmann-Ostenhof</name>
