    <title>The first measurement of $B$ meson semi-leptonic decay contribution to
  non-photonic electrons at RHIC</title>
    <summary>  We present the first measurement for the $B$ meson semi-leptonic decay
contribution to non-photonic electrons at RHIC using non-photonic electron
azimuthal correlations with charged hadrons in p+p collisions at $\sqrt{s_{NN}}
= 200$ GeV from STAR.
