    <title>Recursion relations for Hylleraas three-electron integral</title>
    <summary>  Recursion relations for Hylleraas three-electron integral are obtained in a
closed form by using integration by parts identities. Numerically fast and well
stable algorithm for the calculation of the integral with high powers of
inter-electronic coordinates is presented.
