    <title>Electromagnetic interpretation of leptons</title>
    <summary>  In the previous papers (quant-ph/0204037), (quant-ph/0204134) on the basis of
Dirac's equation we have considered the electromagnetic interpretation of the
quantum theory of electron. Here we continue the electron structure study.
Since the Dirac equation is also the equation of the other leptons, in the
present paper from the electromagnetic point of view we analyse the structure
of neutrino. We will show that not only the electron but also all the other
leptons have the electromagnetic structure.
</summary>
