    <published>2009-10-21T15:08:48Z</published>
    <title>Correspondence on "Electronic correlations in the iron pnictides"</title>
    <summary>  I point out that the observed discrepancy between the measured and calculated
Drude weights in LaFePO may be caused not only by mass renormalization, but
also by a DFT inaccuracy in determining the relative positions of the hole and
electron band.
</summary>
    <author>
      <name>I. I. Mazin</name>
    </author>
    <arxiv:comment xmlns:arxiv="http://arxiv.org/schemas/atom">This correspondence concerns a paper by M. M. Qazilbash, et al,
  Nature Phys. 5, 647 (2009)</arxiv:comment>
