    <title>Exact energy of the spin-polarized two-dimensional electron gas at high
  density</title>
    <summary>  We derive the exact expansion, to $O(r_s)$, of the energy of the high-density
spin-polarized two-dimensional uniform electron gas, where $r_s$ is the Seitz
radius.
</summary>
