    <published>2011-04-19T06:38:34Z</published>
    <title>Two-Center Integrals for r_{ij}^{n} Polynomial Correlated Wave Functions</title>
    <summary>  All integrals needed to evaluate the correlated wave functions with
polynomial terms of inter-electronic distance are included. For this form of
the wave function, the integrals needed can be expressed as a product of
integrals involving at most four electrons.
</summary>
    <author>
      <name>E. V. Rothstein</name>
    </author>
    <arxiv:doi xmlns:arxiv="http://arxiv.org/schemas/atom">10.1103/PhysRevA.3.1581</arxiv:doi>
