    <title>Influence of flavor oscillations on neutrino beam instabilities</title>
    <summary>  We consider the collective neutrino plasma interactions, and study the
electron plasma instabilities produced by a nearly mono-energetic neutrino beam
in a plasma. We describe the mutual influence of neutrino flavor oscillations
and electron plasma waves. We show that the neutrino flavor oscillations are
not only perturbed by electron plasmas waves, but also contribute to the
dispersion relation and the growth rates of neutrino beam instabilities.
