  <entry>
    <id>http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-ph/0212006v2</id>
    <updated>2004-03-01T18:54:47Z</updated>
    <published>2002-11-30T22:31:23Z</published>
    <title>Production and Decay of Excited Electrons at the LHC</title>
    <summary>  We study single production of excited electrons at the CERN LHC through
contact interactions of fermions. Subsequent decays of excited electrons to
ordinary electrons and light fermions via gauge and contact interactions are
examined. The mass range accessible with the ATLAS detector is obtained.
</summary>
